    <text x="400" y="145" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13">Flat rate, separate from other income</text>
    <text x="400" y="170" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13">Requires FIEA reclassification</text>
    <text x="400" y="195" fill="#a1a1aa" font-size="13">Losses carried forward up to 3 years</text>
    <text x="400" y="250" fill="#71717a" font-size="12">ETF listing possible (as early as 2027, per JPX)</text>
    <text x="350" y="170" fill="#fafafa" font-size="22" text-anchor="middle">→</text>
    <text x="30" y="345" fill="#71717a" font-size="12">SBI Securities target: ¥5 trillion (~$32B) AUM within 3 years of launch</text>
    <text x="30" y="368" fill="#71717a" font-size="12">Based on the July 10, 2026 Open QUICK seminar and the April 10 cabinet-approved FIEA bill</text>
  </g>
</svg>
<p style="font-size:11px;color:#52525b;margin-top:-10px">Rates and targets per reported announcements; the bill and tax reform remain under Diet deliberation, not yet finalized.</p>
